{
  "DialogueName": "NewDialogue",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "nodeId": 0,
      "actorId": 0,
      "dialogueText": "你是谁？",
      "nextNodeIndex": 1,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 1,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "你能看到我？",
      "nextNodeIndex": 2,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 2,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "三年了……你是第一个能看见我的。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 3,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 3,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "说出来你不要害怕",
      "nextNodeIndex": 4,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 4,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "我是个鬼呦",
      "nextNodeIndex": 5,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 5,
      "actorId": 0,
      "dialogueText": "……我知道。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 6,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 6,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "别骗人！你要是知道？那你怎么不跑？",
      "nextNodeIndex": 7,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 7,
      "actorId": 0,
      "dialogueText": "。。。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 8,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 8,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "你刚才吃的米饭，是我给的。你放心吃，是正经的米饭，不是泥沙变的，也不是虫子变的。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 9,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 9,
      "actorId": 0,
      "dialogueText": "你为什么要给我吃的",
      "nextNodeIndex": 10,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 10,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "因为……你饿了啊。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 11,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 11,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "饿的人，不该吃饭吗？",
      "nextNodeIndex": 12,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 12,
      "actorId": 0,
      "dialogueText": "那么。。我谢谢你",
      "nextNodeIndex": 13,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 13,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "你可不能白吃呀，你得帮我个忙！",
      "nextNodeIndex": 14,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 14,
      "actorId": 0,
      "dialogueText": "什么忙？能有饭吃，我一定帮！",
      "nextNodeIndex": 15,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 15,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "可是，我快没有米了。。。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 16,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 16,
      "actorId": 0,
      "dialogueText": "为什么？",
      "nextNodeIndex": 17,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 17,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "我不是凭空变出米饭的，我没有那么大的本事",
      "nextNodeIndex": 18,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 18,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "白云浦东边有个朱家庄，庄上有个坏财主，叫朱圆。他家的粮仓里，粮食堆得像山一样高，老鼠在里面打了洞，一年四季都不用愁吃的",
      "nextNodeIndex": 19,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 19,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "给庙里的人吃的米都是从那里拿的。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 20,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 20,
      "actorId": 0,
      "dialogueText": "朱圆发现了？",
      "nextNodeIndex": 21,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 21,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "他请了道士，在粮仓的门上贴了符。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 22,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 22,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "我进不去了。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 23,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 23,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "但是，你虽然身上没有五谷的气味，还能看见我，但你不是鬼，道士的符对你没有用",
      "nextNodeIndex": 24,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 24,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "那符贴在门上，红纸黄字，你一眼就能看见",
      "nextNodeIndex": 26,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 25,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "我叫许秋慈。许是言午许，秋是秋天的秋，慈是慈悲的慈。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 27,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
